318
00:16:52,750 --> 00:16:53,930
Je pozitívny.

319
00:16:54,540 --> 00:16:56,730
To dievča je skutočne Shen Ya Yin.

320
00:16:56,730 --> 00:16:59,420
Je to vaša biologická vnučka.

321
00:17:00,820 --> 00:17:02,080
Dobre.

322
00:17:14,380 --> 00:17:15,540
