354
00:19:02,420 --> 00:19:04,690
Áno, Ya Yin.

355
00:19:10,090 --> 00:19:11,130
Ya Yin?

356
00:19:12,460 --> 00:19:13,970
Takže ty si Ya Yin?

357
00:19:21,220 --> 00:19:23,860
