360
00:19:39,990 --> 00:19:41,720
Si môj dedko.

361
00:19:42,550 --> 00:19:44,140
Dieťa drahé.

362
00:19:47,110 --> 00:19:48,540
Toľko si si toho vytrpela.

363
00:20:04,530 --> 00:20:08,440
