387
00:21:18,800 --> 00:21:19,940
Dobre.

388
00:21:31,490 --> 00:21:32,270
Teta.

389
00:21:34,860 --> 00:21:36,030
Strýko.

390
00:21:38,460 --> 00:21:40,210
Prečo tu nikto nie je?

391
00:21:48,420 --> 00:21:49,380
Ya Yin,

392
00:21:49,380 --> 00:21:52,090
